  <summary date="2021-08-27T14:04:50Z" status="Introduced in House">Isolate COVID-19 Act of 2020

This bill authorizes the Department of Health and Human Services to provide payments to states, tribes, and territories in order to lease hotels to temporarily house individuals with confirmed or presumed cases of COVID-19 who are unable to self-isolate at home and do not need inpatient or outpatient health care.</summary>
